  "appearance": {
    "en": "Deslanoside occurs as colorless or white crys-tals or a white, crystalline powder. It is odorless. It is freely soluble in dehydrated pyridine, sparingly solu-ble in methanol, slightly soluble in ethanol (95), and practi- MS: Amount (mg) of Deslanoside RS taken"
